OverHistory.NewCommentry: Georgina Dempsey to Pratika Rawal Wicket
OverHistory.Commentry: Georgina Dempsey bowling to Pratika Rawal, full length ball, pitching on middle stump, Pratika Rawal plays an aggressive front foot flick WICKET Pratika Rawal lbw Georgina Dempsey (India (Women) 156 Runs for 2 wickets), Appeal from the fielding side
OverHistory.UPDCommentry:
BACK-TO- BACK WICKETS FOR IRELAND! Georgina Dempsey bowling to Pratika Rawal, full length ball, pitching on middle stump, Pratika Rawal trying to go for the flick, ends up getting trapped LBW as she played the wrong line. After consulting with her partner, she decides to review, but the ball tracking showed three reds, and Rawal has to depart after impressive batting. Both the openers are back in the hut.

WICKET Pratika Rawal lbw Georgina Dempsey (India (Women) 156 Runs for 2 wickets)
